parameters:
I have already cleared this event. Would you like to do
the event again?
Commonly seen light bulbs and tables.

...I thought, but it's a decorative book and all the
contents are blank.
It seems that the signal doesn't reach.
The antenna is dead! It's gone!

There is a tabletop plant pot and a photo of this cottage
placed.
Are you really going back to the title?
The wardrobe is big for a private room.
The wardrobe is big for a private room.
...I don't really want to open it.
...I don't really want to open it.
Commonly seen light bulbs and tables.
I don't really want to do it right now.
The mirror is being wiped clean.
Shower head with water falling from above.
Shower head with water falling from above.
Lying down on the bed makes me feel sleepy...
I'm already tired even though I haven't done anything.
What should I do? Should I take a nap?
As soon as I lie down, I fall fast asleep.
Yeah, it's not time to sleep yet.
Why is it in my hand...?
Hey, Hikaru. Did you take a nap?

Since it seems like we'll have to be here for a while, I
thought we could divide up some roles amongst ourselves.
Hmm... But why are we suddenly dividing up the roles?
...Did you try the food that Kanae made yesterday?

I was thinking, how about each of us do what we're good
at?

Honestly, I wanted Tsugumi to be in charge of cooking, so that's
why I suggested dividing the roles.

You're free. Since you're the closest to the girls, if you
think they're having a hard time, go and help them.

Hahaha. A beginner on the tight end? It's going to be
difficult.

No worries, just talking to myself. Some of them can be kinda
sensitive, so take care of them for me.

Also... if you want to date one of them,
this might be your chance.

In my opinion, the mood has been good here for the
past few weeks, so now is the perfect timing.
If a hole exists, it's a man's nature to make it a goal. Hahaha.

For the first time, Senpai looks like an older brother I
can respect.
What, until now I wasn't an older brother you could respect?

(I thought you were someone like a delinquent from the
sports club...!)

I couldn't help but be impressed by this man with a heart
as broad as the sea taking care of their juniors.
Loyalty, you have my loyalty, Shogun Senpai...!

As I thought so, I gave one Hikaru point in my heart
to Senpai.

There's no need to deliberately stop your junior from trying
out romance.
Only if it's Saruyama, I might be a little troubled.

The moment that guy causes a commotion about forming
couples within the group, this group is definitely
going to explode.
I can't let it end with my generation.

Well, um... He's not a bad person, but... I also have the
position of being the club president.
Anyway, I'll leave it to you.

Kenta and I will take a look around the back mountains, so
you stay down around here.
If there's anything dangerous, report it immediately.

Hmm... It seems like my antenna got blown away by the typhoon
and flew somewhere.

I think if I fix the antenna, it might turn into a
phone.

If there are any suspicious items, please check them just
in case.
Senpai doesn't seem to have much confidence.

Well... even if they are a senior, there isn't much of an
age difference.

This kind of situation is something even Senpai is
experiencing for the first time.
First, let's take a look around.
Maybe I'll take a short break for now...
